# AUDIT

Chronological log of meaningful macro actions on this orchestrator.
Append-only. Every closing skill (or manual durable action) writes
one line here.

The point is one-glance history. Git log is the ground truth for
file changes; this is the human-readable layer above it.

> See `.claude/orchestrator-rules.md` "Audit log discipline" for the
> exact format and emoji set.

---

## Emoji legend

- 📦 Migration shipped / closed
- 📜 ADR filed
- 🏗 Feature plan filed
- ⚠️ Risk surfaced / accepted
- 🛡 Risk mitigated
- 🔥 Incident opened
- 🩹 Incident resolved (postmortem filed)
- 🚀 Cross-repo deploy / coordinated release
- 🎯 Review completed (weekly / monthly / quarterly)
- 🔧 Macro state refreshed (`/audit` phase, etc.)
- 🤝 Sub-repo registered / deregistered

